==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Giver
<hw>Giv"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who gives; a donor;
a bestower; a grantor; one who imparts or distributes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It is the <qex>giver</qex>, and not the gift, that engrosses the
heart of the Christian.</q> <rj><qau>Kollock.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gives</ent>⟦br⟧
